                    <h2>Travel Information to Chhindwara</h2>
                    <p>Chhindwara can be approached by road from Nagpur (distance 127 kms.), Jabalpur (distance 197 kms.), or Bhopal (distance 278 kms.). Taxis and buses are readily available from these cities to Chhindwara.</p>
                    <p>So after reaching any of these major cities, you can take a bus to Chhindwara. From Chhindwara bus station, you can grab a taxi to the Puja Venue: Linga Aashram, Chhindwara.</p>
                    
