                            <p>Take a flight to any of the nearest International Airports among Nagpur, Bhopal, or Jabalpur. From Nagpur, Bhopal, or Jabalpur, catch a bus for Chhindwara. Take a cab or auto-rickshaw to the Linga Aashram.</p>
                        </div>
        
                        <div class="transport-method">
